snippet: In the first five days of the United States Olympic swimming trials, with high-tech swimsuits out, only three American records fell while every world record remained standing.
lead_paragraph: In the first five days of the United States Olympic swimming trials, with high-tech swimsuits out, only three American records fell while every world record remained standing.
